Description: Linux notification filter with a GUI rule editor
 Shush monitors desktop notifications via D-Bus and suppresses everything
 except those matching user-defined keyword rules. Features a full PyQt5
 GUI for managing per-person and per-app rules, a live activity log,
 focus-mode presets, and system tray integration.
